my change over time, but for now this how

00:05:19.050 --> 00:05:25.540
I feel about the characteristics and usefulness
of the weapons available so far, with that

00:05:25.540 --> 00:05:31.830
being said it's now time again to pick a best
and worst gun in this category.

00:05:31.830 --> 00:05:40.060
So my favourite handgun is a bit of a tricky
one as the first 3 pistols are all very similar,

00:05:40.060 --> 00:05:46.870
I'll rule out the grach as it feels to me
near identical to the P226 except for being

00:05:46.870 --> 00:05:55.520
slightly worse in most if not all areas, next
the M9A1, this is the most accessible for

00:05:55.520 --> 00:06:01.039
people not used to using a pistol and is one
of the most enjoyable to use but lacks the

00:06:01.039 --> 00:06:08.180
power accuracy and range of the P226, so as
you've already guessed the best gun in this

00:06:08.180 --> 00:06:14.219
class is the P226 which is outstanding in
all areas.

00:06:14.219 --> 00:06:20.360
As for the worst, this is a battle between
the magnum and the PDW as both aren't that

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:27.340
useful due to either ridiculous recoil or
a slow fire rate, however I'd have to give

00:06:27.340 --> 00:06:32.700
the wooden spoon to the PDW as at least the
novelty factor of the magnum makes it fun

00:06:32.700 --> 00:06:33.700
